          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="bg-tossup/10 border border-tossup/30 rounded-lg p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-tossup">
          Not sure what's on your ballot? Use
          <a href="/find-your-ballot" class="underline">Find Your Ballot</a>
          to see what races are in your state, or check the
          <a href="/calendar" class="underline">election calendar</a>
          for your primary date.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
